description: Episode 4: 'The Beach House' The majestic wonder of the Northern Californian coast has drawn lovers to its shores for centuries. Jacob (Jeremy Bilding) and Brett (Trent Locke), for example. They are seemingly inseparable, bound to each other like the sky holds on to the clouds. But in a land of impulse and desire, the hunger for more is all but undeniable, even for the most loyal of lovers. On this journey, the hunt to satisfy the irresistible craving brings them to a street hustler named Marc (Christian Wilde), here on the streets of San Francisco.
title: Golden Gate Season 01
